{"tid":2438623,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"龜龜眼眶/眼皮有粒白點","createTime":"2021-03-08T15:27:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T21:57:45.000Z","uid":105197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d237878a88f3a0b5ac5980e2f4e7d47c4fa027fc","tid":2438623,"uid":105197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T15:27:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1iO5BKz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1iO5BKz.jpg&h=0ad3c96c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢隻左眼嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，今日見佢淨係合埋左眼，<br />\n擘大右眼，先知佢生咗粒嘢咁(唔似黐住污糟嘢?)<br />\n<br />\n有無養龜巴絲知道咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />google過下 但唔似咩白眼症<br />\n諗住聽日帶去睇醫生，但想知道咩事先<br />\n養咗好多年 擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d227f1185555505a9f3e6c423f4bbf99c4817dfa","tid":2438623,"uid":105197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T15:54:23.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb5be50596b3444e291cfb72728a8949bae0864","tid":2438623,"uid":222787,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T16:03:26.000Z","msg":"幫推 祝龜龜身體健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c5452658bf962031cbf7c1dbb37a9b5fb9769a","tid":2438623,"uid":123696,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T16:04:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2a2b8f12ec5a3f1ce7d3f6497de3bf50237caa","tid":2438623,"uid":105197,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"47c5452658bf962031cbf7c1dbb37a9b5fb9769a","tid":2438623,"uid":123696,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T16:04:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T16:05:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asse